\newlabel{tab:bench}{{2}{9}{Strict-scorer results on 59 unique BioBench roots using the reference Open-Rosalind pipeline on Gemma. Trace completeness remains saturated, but accuracy drops materially on Edge inputs, making the benchmark more discriminative than the original loose dashboard scorer.\relax }{table.caption.6}{}}
