\newlabel{tab:ablation}{{3}{10}{Aggregate six-model ablation over 59 unique tasks and five conditions (1,770 runs total). The strongest and most stable effect is the drop from \texttt {full} to \texttt {no\_tool}; citation and template ablations change accountability properties much more than average accuracy.\relax }{table.caption.7}{}}
